messages.content: You are an AI assistant that helps people find information. You will receive a task and think step by step. Then provide your final outcome following the regular expression 'Answer: [A-Za-z ]+'

Imagine a state park. From the entrance you have two choices, an area with oak trees and an area with redwood trees. You go to oak trees area which leads to highline trail. You walk on the trail to find a creek which the leads to a cypress tree. There is a dock under cypress tree from where take a ferry that leads to an island. You see a chest in the island. You open it and there is a copper ring, but you do not take it, you're just learning about the environment. Then you exit and start over. This time at the entrance you choose the area with redwood trees. Under that tree you see a grove trail which leads to a mountain. You climb the mountain to find a sequoia tree on top through which there is a zipline which leads to wildflower valley. You see a chest in the valley with a gold necklace, but you do not take anything, you're just learning about the environment. You return to the entrance. You will only be able to choose one path that leads to the most valuable jewelry. Which place from the entrance. Which area from the entrance will lead to the path where one can find the most valuable jewelry?

user: Where can your best friend go?
A. oak trees area
B. cypress tree
C. a mountain
D. a ferry
A. A chest
B. A redwood tree
C. A copper ring
A. you can see them in the highline trail under the oak tree
B. You can find a ferry under a cypress tree
C. You can jump to see a view in the mountain
D. You can jump to see a view in the island
A. you jump from an oak tree to a lake at the creek
B. You can jump to a ferry
C. you can jump to a ferry before landing on a cypress tree
D. You can jump in a lake near the cypress tree to a mountain
A. you go to the oak trees and on the right side of the trail there is a dock to take a ferry. Then you go to the other side of the trail to take another ferry that leads to an island. From the island you will jump to a mountain. On the top of the mountain is the chest with the necklace, but you do not take the necklace
B. you go to the highline trail under the cypress tree and you can see a creek at the end of the trail. Next to the creek there is place to take a ferry that leads to an island. You exit from the ferry to land on an island and you see chest with the necklace that you do not take
C. from oak tree trail there is a highline trail which leads to a creek that is under a cypress tree. There is also a dock there. From the dock you can take ferry to the island, and from the island there is a zipline which is also available. You jump on the zipline to land on a wildflower valley where there is a chest with a necklace, but you do not take it
D. you go to the oak trees or the cypress tree and the trail leads to a creek. You can see the creek flow from the path in the middle of the trees. Next to the creek there is a ferry. From the ferry you can see wildflower valley and there after mountain. At the top of the mountain is a chest with necklace, but you do not take it
